*C2. Tim in Trouble
*C3. On the Road to the North
*C4. Riding into Danger
*C5. Mandrake&#x27;s Castle
*C6. Escape by Night
*C7. Three Fires on the Dark Tower
*C8. Tim Rides on the Ghost Bus

===Series D===
